Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=10}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:53.51,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{There once was a man\Nnamed Montblanc Noland, -OG}Em algum lugar no North Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:56.01,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{from a kingdom in the northern seas. -OG}havia um homem chamado\NMont Blanc Noland.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:02:03.56,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{Noland the Explorer always told\Nstories of incredible adventures. -OG}Noland era um explorador que sempre\Nfalava de suas aventuras fantásticas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:09.90,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas os aldeões nunca conseguiam\Ndizer se eram verdade ou não.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:15.87,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,Um dia, Noland retornou de\Numa viagem e relatou ao rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:19.54,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela se ergue ainda mais orgulhosa\Ne bela em ruínas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.33,0:02:22.04,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{This city is named Shandia! -OG}{The city is called Shandora! -T}O nome da cidade é Shandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:26.00,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{The term\N"city of gold" fits it like none other! -OG}{The name\N"City of Gold" fits it like no other! -T}É a própria definição\Nde "Cidade do Ouro."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:33.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Marie Jois has finally granted us\Npermission to enter the Grand Line.}Mary Geoise finalmente nos concedeu\Npermissão para entrar na Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:37.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sendo assim, desejo enviá-lo\Nem outra missão.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:38.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes, it would be my pleasure! -OG}Será um prazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:45.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But, I've decided my soldiers will\Njoin you on this journey, as will I. -OG}{However, I've decided that my soldiers\Nwill join you on this journey, as will I. -T}{\q2}Porém, decidi que meus soldados\Ne eu nos juntaremos a você nesta jornada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entendido?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:47.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:52.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kalgara!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:53.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seto...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:55.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai tocar o sino, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:56.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu ajudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Nola.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:03.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You've sure\Nsettled into these ruins! -OG}{You've really\Nmade these ruins your home. -T}Você realmente se acomodou\Nnessas ruínas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:09.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Say! When do you suppose\NNoland[-san] and the others will come? -OG}{Say! When do you suppose\NNoland and his crew will come? -Z}Ei! Quando será que\NNoland e sua tripulação vão voltar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:13.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's all you ever ask\Nwhen you come here. -OG}Você pergunta isso toda vez\Nque vem aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não vai ser tão fácil\Npra ele voltar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele nasceu nos mares do extremo norte.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele também tem uma família em casa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:24.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas ele prometeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:29.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{As long as we keep ringing this bell\Nhere, he'll show up sooner or later. -OG}Enquanto continuarmos tocando este sino,\Nele vai aparecer cedo ou tarde.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's this?! -OG}O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso parece ruim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Come, Seto! We have\Nto protect the village! -OG}{Come, Seto! We must\Nprotect the village! -T}Venha, Seto! Proteja a aldeia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.64,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.81,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que a ilha acaba\Nde repente aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:12.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Damn you! -OG}Seu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você mentiu pra mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:18.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Onde está esse ouro seu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:20.53,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra onde foi a aldeia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:23.95,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu com esta ilha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.37,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Kalgara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.58,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Se você está vivo, me deixe ouvir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.46,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,O som do sino de ouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:32.63,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,942)}{Answer me, fire of Shandia! -OG}Me responda, Luz de Shandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:39.01,Main-207-,,0,0,12,,{Noland's public\Nexecution's about to start! -OG}A execução pública de Noland\Nestá prestes a começar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! Por aqui, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seis anos atrás,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:48.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,eu vi uma enorme cidade de ouro\Nna ilha de Jaya na Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:52.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The City of Gold does exist! -OG}A Cidade do Ouro existe! Eu juro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:55.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então vamos ouvir\Num dos seus tripulantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Este homem está dizendo a verdade?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No. It's an absolute lie. -OG}Não. É uma mentira total.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:05.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Eh?! Noland[-san] is a liar?! -OG}O quê?! Noland é um mentiroso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then were all his stories fake?! -OG}Então... todas as histórias dele eram falsas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que absurdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:12.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele mentiu pro reino inteiro\Ne se fez de herói!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:16.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Who's that witness?!\NHe's not part of our crew! -OG}Quem é aquela testemunha?!\NEle não faz parte da nossa tripulação!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did you see Kalgara and the others?! -OG}Vocês viram o Kalgara\Ne os aldeões?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:21.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Commodore! What happened?! -OG}Comodoro! O que\Naconteceu lá fora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:22.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Prendam-nos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Men... -OG}{My men... -T}{My crew... -T}Vocês...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por suas mentiras hediondas,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:37.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mont Blanc Noland é sentenciado\Nà morte por decapitação!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mentiroso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:43.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Ele é um mentiroso!\N– Mentiroso!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:46.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The commodore'd never lie! -OG}O comodoro jamais mentiria!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:47.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Comodoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:06:00.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Liar! Liar! Liar! Liar!... -OG}{Liar! Liar! Liar! Liar...! -T}– Mentiroso! Mentiroso!\N– Mentiroso! Mentiroso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:46.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deus! É uma ilha gigante de vearth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes. Did you hear that? -OG}De fato. Você ouviu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The singing voice of\Nthis beautiful vearth... -OG}Essa é a voz cantante\Ndesta gloriosa vearth...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:54.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It is truly the birth of holy land. -OG}{It is truly the birth of a holy land. -T}Isso realmente é o nascimento de uma terra sagrada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:58.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É lá que eu devo viver!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:03.69,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:07.37,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{What is this?! I can't breathe well! -OG}{What's this?! I can barely breathe! -Polly}O que está acontecendo?!\NMal consigo respirar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:08.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Todos estão bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Recomponham-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Pull yourselves together! -OG}Acordem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cuidem dos feridos! Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:16.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kalgara! Invasores!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:19.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I hereby claim this Vearth\Nas mine! -OG}Eu reivindico esta vearth como minha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:21.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Deus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deus é o cacete!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Stop them, warriors! -OG}Segurem eles, guerreiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We cannot let this\Nland be taken away! -OG}Não podemos deixar esta\Nterra ser tomada de nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.85,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Fizemos uma promessa, Noland...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:39.11,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,de que nos encontraríamos de novo um dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.98,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Kalgara...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.32,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Where are you?! -OG}Pra onde você foi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:49.03,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{When you return to Jaya, what will\Nyou think when you see we're gone? -OG}Quando você voltar a Jaya, o que vai\Npensar quando ver que não estamos mais lá?
Comment: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:56.29,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Hold on a little longer!\NI'll let you know that "we are here"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.62,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Aguente mais um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.62,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll let you know that "we are here"!}Vou enviar uma mensagem de que...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:56.29,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hold on a little longer!\NI'll let you know that "we are here"! -OG}{we're still here! -Polly}nós estamos aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:58.79,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Você está vivo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:01.54,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Tenho tanta coisa pra te contar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:03.84,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Kalgara...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:08.26,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm only concerned\Nfor your well-being... -OG}{My only concern is your well-being... -T}Eu só quero saber se você está bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:13.76,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's meet again on the\Nsame land someday, Noland! -OG}{Let's meet at this place\Nagain someday, Noland! -Polly+Matt+T}{Let's meet here again\Nsomeday, Noland! -Polly}Vamos nos encontrar nesta mesma terra\Nde novo um dia, Noland!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:18.06,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Light the fire of Shandia! -OG}{Ring the Light of Shandora! -T}Brilhem a Luz de Shandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:22.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Grande Guerreiro Kalgara\Ncontinuou a gritar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:24.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just once would've been enough. -OG}{Just once would've been enough, -T}Uma única vez seria o bastante...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:31.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{For he believed the fire of Shandia\Nwould echo and let all know that, -OG}pois ele acreditava que a Luz de Shandora\Necoaria e deixaria todos saberem:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:34.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós estamos aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:38.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{But the bell never once rang. -OG}Porém, o sino nunca tocou uma única vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:44.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everything was later told to our\Nvillage by sailors from the Blue Sea. -OG}{Our village heard about it later,\Nfrom sailors of the Blue Sea. -T}{Blue Sea sailors later came up\Nand told our village everything. -Z}Depois, marinheiros do Blue Sea vieram\Naté a aldeia e nos contaram tudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:48.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Noland, to whom we owe so much,\Nhad such pride for our city -OG}{Noland, to whom we owe our lives,\Nhad so much pride for our city -T}Noland, a quem devemos\Ntanto, morreu marcado como mentiroso...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:55.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{that he refused to deny Shandia's\Nexistence and died known as a liar. -OG}{that he refused to deny Shandora's\Nexistence and thus died as a liar. -T}{that he refused to deny Shandora's\Nexistence and died known as a liar. -T}{his pride in our city so strong that\Nhe refused to deny Shandora's existence! -T}tudo porque ele tinha tanto orgulho da nossa cidade\Nque se recusou a negar a existência de Shandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:58.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas já era tarde demais,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:04.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,pois o Grande Guerreiro Kalgara havia morrido\Nhonrosamente em batalha aqui no céu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,sem nunca conseguir\Ntransmitir sua mensagem...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:07.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That -OG}Esse...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{is Great Warrior\NKalgara's greatest regret. -OG}é o arrependimento do Grande Guerreiro Kalgara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você acha que ainda poderia alcançá-lo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:15.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquele sino!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:18.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se o tocássemos agora,\No som chegaria até Noland?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Boa pergunta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:25.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,978)}{We are close to Heaven...}Nós estamos perto do céu aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:31.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wyper! We'll die if\Nwe don't escape now! -OG}Wyper! Vamos morrer se não corrermos agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wyper...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:37.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Enel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem te deu o direito\Nde tirar tudo de nós?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:48.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Este é o céu! O domínio de Deus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everything is an eyesore! -OG}Tudo é uma praga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:55.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,As pessoas, as árvores, a terra!\NVoltem de onde vieram!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:58.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let everything rain into the Blue Sea! -OG}Que tudo caia no Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Angel Island não vai durar muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tem muita gente ferida!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:12.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Get them into boats,\Nthen give them first aid! -OG}Coloquem-nos num barco\Ne deem primeiros socorros!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:13.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Corram!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{– Hurry!\N– Hurry, into the ocean! -OG}{– Hurry!\N– Hurry, to the ocean! -T}– Rápido!\N– Rápido, pro mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:22.69,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I get chills when I imagine that\Ngirl's speech being any later! -OG}{I get chills imagining that\Ngirl's speech being any later! -T}Se o discurso daquela garota tivesse sido\Num segundo mais tarde...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:24.44,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela está bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:42.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The scurrying angels are like a\Nline of ants that's been disturbed! -OG}{The scurrying angels look like\Na line of ants that's been disturbed! -T}Vejam como os anjos correm\Ncomo formigas perturbadas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:47.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Return to where you belong, Skypiea! -OG}{Return to your rightful place, Skypiea! -T}{Return from whence\Nyou came, Skypiea! -Z}Volte à sua forma original, Skypiea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que é aquilo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um buraco no White-White Sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:58.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I have no need for good\Nold God's Shrine either! -OG}{I have no need for\Nthis old temple either! -Polly}{Though nostalgic, I have no need\Nfor this old temple either! -Rin+Z}Também não preciso deste\Nvelho templo sentimental!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:06.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nor for the city of Shandia below it! -OG}Nem da cidade de Shandora abaixo dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:21.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There is but one thing left\Nin this land that I want! -OG}Só resta uma coisa nesta\Nterra que eu desejo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The golden grand belfry! -OG}{The grand golden belfry! -T}O grande sino dourado!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:28.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Two voices, at this final stage? -OG}Mesmo agora, ainda restam duas vozes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Caramba! Como ele corre tão rápido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:33.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami! Be all right! -OG}Nami! É bom que esteja bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:38.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And I won't let you have\Nthe golden bell, Enel! -OG}Não vou deixar você ficar\Ncom aquele sino dourado, Enel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:53.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What is it Enel wants there? -OG}O que é que Enel quer lá em cima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A gold bell at the top. -OG}{A gold bell at the very top. -T}Um sino dourado bem no topo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:57.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um sino...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A gold bell? -OG}Um sino dourado?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:03.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is that what you said?! -OG}Foi isso que você disse antes, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wyper...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:05.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:08.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,D-D-Do que vocês estão\Nfalando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:15.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You also spoke of the bell before\Nbeing hit by Enel's electric attack. -OG}Você também falou do sino antes\Nde Enel te eletrocutar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:17.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So he's going after it? -OG}Então é isso que ele quer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Onde exatamente está?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is no time for that! -OG}Não tem tempo pra isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:25.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você viu aquele raio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:28.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos morrer se não\Nsairmos daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:34.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Somewhere near the top\Nof this giant vine. -OG}Está em algum lugar perto\Ndo topo deste cipó gigante.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como?! Como você sabe disso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:37.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:41.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We promised we'd wait\Nfor Nami back on our ship! -OG}Prometemos que esperaríamos\NA Nami no navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:46.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She's gonna be back\Nwith Luffy any time now! -OG}{She'll be back with\NLuffy any moment now! -Z}Ela vai voltar com\No Luffy a qualquer momento!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele tem razão, Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:51.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The ruins of Shandia in\Nthe layer below us... -OG}As ruínas de Shandora\Nna camada abaixo de nós...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:55.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This vine pierces right through\Nthe very center of the city. -OG}Este cipó atravessa\No centro da cidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:59.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh, geez! Look! -OG}Ei! Olha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:03.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I dunno if it's ruins or what,\Nbut it's been blasted to pieces! -OG}Ruínas ou não, foi\Nexplodido em pedaços!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:08.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We could be next, you know! -OG}{And we might be next! -T}{And we could very well\Nbe next, you know! -Polly}E nós podemos ser os próximos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:13.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A map I found in the ruins\Nindicated that the grand belfry -OG}{I found a map in the ruins\Nwhich suggested the grand belfry -Polly}Encontrei um mapa nas ruínas\Nque indicava que a torre do sino
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:16.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{that held the golden bell was\Nlocated in the city's center. -OG}{that held the golden bell\Nstood in the city's center. -T}ficava no centro da cidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:20.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Em outras palavras, o impacto de\Nser lançada pra cima pelo cipó
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:23.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,pode ter jogado o sino\Nainda mais alto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:39.80,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! -OG}E aí, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:48.27,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\t(3605,0,1,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&)}{The City of Gold has a huge bell, right? -OG}Tem um sino enorme\Nna Cidade do Ouro, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:57.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now, then. I'm above Giant Jack. -OG}Agora, então. Subi\Nacima do Giant Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:04.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I doubt anyone would come searching for something in these skies above God's Shrine. -OG}Duvido que alguém procuraria\Nnos céus acima do Santuário de Deus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mesmo depois de 400 anos...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now, then. -OG}Agora, então. Onde será?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Onde está o sino dourado...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que lugar é esse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Him... -OG}{That guy... -T}Ele de novo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:40.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou impressionado que ele chegou aqui\Ncom aquele peso preso.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aí está você!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:49.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espere aí! Enel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que praga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wyper! What are you planning to do?! -OG}Wyper! O que você está tentando fazer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não me diga que você vai\Nescalar o cipó?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Todos! Afastem-se do cipó!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Algo está caindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:38.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A ponta do cipó?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What happened above?! -OG}O que aconteceu lá em cima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:44.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! Não me digam que\NLuffy e Nami caíram com ele?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:50.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No! You can't in your\Ncondition! -OG}Para! Você não pode ir assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você está todo arrebentado!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:57.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And even if you do climb up, there's\Nno way to reach Enel in the sky! -OG}{And even if you do climb up, you have\Nno way to reach Enel in the sky! -T}E mesmo que consiga subir,\Nvocê não tem como alcançar Enel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:58.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's directly above! -OG}Está bem acima de nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:08.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}O sino que o Grande Guerreiro Kalgara buscava!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:21.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como pretende escalar\Naté aqui nesse estado?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:24.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:29.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fique aí por um tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:33.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou te mostrar algo interessante.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:43.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:50.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh, right! I gotta figure\Nsomething out while he's gone! -OG}Ah, é! Tenho que resolver\Nisso enquanto ele não está!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:10.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:14.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ioiô!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:23.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que ele está fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All right! I'm back on track! -OG}Certo! Voltei aos trilhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:34.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora é minha chance de embarcar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:40.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Finalmente te alcancei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:43.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Eh? Nami! What're you doing here?! -OG}Hã? Nami! O que você está fazendo aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vim te buscar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:49.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sanji[-kun] and Usopp saved me,\Nso I was down below! -OG}{Thanks to Sanji and Usopp,\NI was able to get down safely! -T}Desci em segurança\Ngraças ao Sanji e ao Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Really?! You were?! -OG}Sério?! Desceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:54.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas mais importante...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:57.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:00.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que é aquilo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:08.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,As nuvens de trovão estão\Nmudando de forma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The sky! -OG}Lá no céu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:19.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– O céu está escuro!\N– Isso é ruim! Nos salvem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Mamãe!\N– O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:24.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Into the ocean! Quickly! -OG}{To the ocean! Quickly! -T}Pro mar! Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:29.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tem uma bola gigante flutuando no céu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquela coisa é má notícia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:40.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É uma nuvem de trovão envolta\Nnum manto esférico...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:44.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and it's packed with intense currents\Nand internal electric discharges! -OG}repleta de correntes intensas\Ne descargas elétricas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:19:00.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Está bem acima de Angel Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,As nuvens de trovão ficaram esféricas...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:06.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Th-This is a nightmare! -OG}I-Isso tem que ser um pesadelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This isn't\Nsomething you see in real life! -OG}Não tem como isso ser real!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:15.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que mais ele está\Nplanejando soltar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:23.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hurry! Into the ocean! -OG}{Hurry! To the ocean! -T}O mar! Pro mar, rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:24.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:36.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now you will learn that\Nthe heavens are mine! -OG}Está na hora de aprenderem que\Nos céus pertencem a mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:42.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{With the Maxim and my power, -OG}Somente com a Arca Maxim\Ne meu poder divino
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I can accomplish such acts of God! -OG}{can I accomplish such acts of God! -T}{can I accomplish this miraculous task! -Rin}posso realizar atos tão divinos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:47.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olhem isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:49.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Está caindo sobre Angel Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:52.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É tarde demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:54.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não vamos conseguir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:55.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Corram! Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou com medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:07.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Raigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No, this can't be! -OG}Não, isso não pode ser real!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did the White Berets\Nmanage to escape? -OG}Os White Berets também escaparam?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:42.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The White Berets saved us... -OG}Eles nos salvaram...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The island we were born on and our\Nhometown are completely gone!}{The island where we were born...\Nand our hometown. They're gone! -T}A ilha onde nascemos...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The island we were born on and our\Nhometown are completely gone!}{The island where we were born...\Nand our hometown. They're gone! -T}Nossa cidade natal...\NDesapareceram completamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:55.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Até as nuvens do mar foram destruídas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:03.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que visão maravilhosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:06.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É assim que o céu deveria ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:14.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{W-What was that explosion?! -OG}Q-Que explosão foi aquela?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:19.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And the thunderbolts\Nare still raining down?! -OG}{Thunderbolts are still\Ncoming down like rain too! -Polly+Viz}Raios ainda estão\Ncaindo como chuva!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:22.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I don't get the feeling\NI'll be leaving alive now! -OG}Tenho a sensação de que\Nnão vou sair vivo daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:27.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele erradicou Angel Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How can you be so ruthless, Enel?! -OG}Como você pode...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:36.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como você pode ser tão cruel, Enel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:42.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What loud rumbling... -OG}{What a loud rumble... -T}Que estrondo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:45.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Temos que esperar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:49.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We have to take them\Nback to the Blue Sea! -OG}{We have to bring them\Nback to the Blue Sea! -T}Temos que levá-los\Nde volta ao Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:53.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Suba pra gente\Ndescer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:56.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everyone's headed for our ship! -OG}Todos estão indo pro Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:58.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A gente também precisa ir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:21:59.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não posso.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:03.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não pode? Por quê?!\NDo que está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:05.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even if I don't have to save you now... -OG}{Even if I no longer have to save you... -T}Mesmo que você não\Nprecise mais ser salva...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:08.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu ainda tenho assuntos pendentes aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:11.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Unfinished business? What could\Nyou possibly have left to do here?! -OG}"Pendentes"? O que você ainda\Npode ter pra fazer aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:13.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you trying to get back\Nat Enel or something?! -OG}Está tentando se vingar do Enel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:16.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's a gold bell up above! -OG}{There's a golden bell above us! -T}Tem um sino dourado no céu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:20.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Gold? -OG}Um dourado...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.49,0:22:23.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Your life is more important, you know! Just look!}{Your life is more important\Nthan that! Just look around! -T}Sua vida é mais importante\Nque isso! Olha ao redor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:26.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que raios não te machuquem,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:30.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{he has the power to destroy\Neverything in other ways! -OG}Enel tem o poder de destruir\Ntudo ao seu redor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:33.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If it's gold you want, then look!\NYou have some on your arm! -OG}{If it's gold you want, you\Nalready have some on your arm! -T}Se você quer ouro,\Nolha pro seu braço!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:36.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Forget about some gold bell! -OG}Esquece esse sino dourado!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:38.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You'll be killed! -OG}{You're gonna be killed! -T}Você vai morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:40.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou morrer...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:41.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Dá pra parar?! Você–
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:43.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você mesma viu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:46.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vi o quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:54.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The city of gold... it existed! -OG}{The City of Gold... it exists! -T}A Cidade do Ouro... É real de verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:01.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It wasn't a lie. -OG}Ele não estava mentindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:05.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Old diamond-head's ancestor... -OG}{Old chestnut head's ancestor... -Z}O ancestral do cabeça de castanha...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:09.95,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Se estiver lá, ótimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:12.29,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Se não estiver, tudo bem também.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:15.79,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Não é que eu queira\Nprovar a inocência dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:22.09,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,É um duelo com o homem\Nque arruinou minha vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:25.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\t(1774,0,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}{He wasn't lying. -OG}Ele estava dizendo a verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:30.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So I have to let the old guy\Nand the others below know... -OG}Então tenho que avisar o cabeça\Nde castanha e os outros lá embaixo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:35.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{that the city of gold was in the sky! -OG}que a Cidade do Ouro está no céu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:40.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If I ring the bell... -OG}Se eu tocar aquele sino...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:43.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,eles devem conseguir ouvir!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:49.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Senão, vão continuar procurando\Nno fundo do mar até morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:55.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:59.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não posso deixar Enel ficar com ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:04.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure the huge bell can\Nbe heard from anywhere... -OG}Tenho certeza que um sino desse tamanho\Npode ser ouvido de qualquer lugar...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.05,0:24:10.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{so that's why I'm going\Nto ring the gold bell! -OG}é por isso que eu vou\Ntocar aquele sino dourado!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.06,0:24:18.69,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! The City of Gold\Nhas a huge bell, right? -OG}Tem um sino enorme\Nna Cidade do Ouro, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.19,0:24:24.40,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes, Noland's logbook did mention it had one. -OG}Sim, o diário de bordo de Noland\Nmencionava um.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.78,0:24:26.28,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que a pergunta?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.28,0:24:27.86,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,É, por quê?
Comment: 0,0:24:24.78,0:24:27.86,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,– Why do you ask?\N– Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.55,0:24:32.99,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I thought up a good idea! -OG}Acabei de ter uma boa ideia!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.99,0:24:34.58,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê? O que é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.37,0:24:38.62,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Se a gente tocasse aquele sino enorme...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.62,0:24:42.88,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{do you think old diamond-head and\Nthe monkeys below would hear it? -OG}{do you think old chestnut head and\Nthe monkeys below would hear it? -Z}vocês acham que o cabeça de castanha\Ne os macacos lá embaixo ouviriam?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.59,0:24:47.97,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{They'd hear it, right? -OG}Com certeza ouviriam, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.39,0:24:53.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quando ele diz que vai\Nfazer algo, ele faz.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.64,0:24:56.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então, ele está...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.35,0:24:58.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele realmente disse isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.23,0:25:00.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas dada a situação...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.94,0:25:05.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's going to ring the bell, you say?! -OG}O sino...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.61,0:25:07.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's going to ring the bell, you say?! -OG}Ele realmente vai tocá-lo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.32,0:25:12.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É. Mesmo que Nami tente\Ntrazê-lo de volta, ele não vem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.03,0:25:17.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Because he's after\Nthe same thing Enel is. -OG}Porque ele e Enel\Nestão atrás da mesma coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.59,0:25:28.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Consegui!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.93,0:25:36.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem te deu permissão\Npra embarcar neste navio?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.51,0:25:37.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Enel!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.40,0:25:50.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{See! I told you it was a bad idea! -OG}Luffy! Eu disse que era péssima ideia!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.74,0:25:51.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Damn him! -OG}Dane-se ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.32,0:25:54.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E então?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:58.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did you see the silly little\Nisland vanish from the sky? -OG}{Did you see that stupid\Nlittle island vanish from the sky? -T}Viu aquela ilhazinha idiota\Ndesaparecer do céu?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.29,0:26:00.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Girl. -OG}Você, garota.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.66,0:26:05.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I assume you're not going\Nto try and sweet-talk me -OG}Posso presumir que não quer\Nmais tentar me convencer
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.04,0:26:07.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{by asking me to take you\Nto Endless Vearth again... -OG}{into taking you to\NEndless Vearth again? -T}a te levar pra\NEndless Vearth de novo?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.63,0:26:08.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.46,0:26:12.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Assim que eu tiver o que quero,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.59,0:26:18.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I will destroy all of Skypiea\Nwith this next Raigo! -OG}vou destruir toda Skypiea\Ncom meu próximo Raigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.01,0:26:21.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No one can be allowed to escape now! -OG}{No one will be able to escape now! -T}Ninguém vai conseguir escapar agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.06,0:26:30.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Including the several unmoving\Nvoices directly below you! -OG}Nem mesmo as poucas vozes\Nlogo abaixo de você!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.69,0:26:31.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Logo abaixo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.57,0:26:36.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm going to eradicate this land\Nthat is out of place in the sky -OG}{I'm going to eradicate this land\Nthat has no place in the sky -T}Vou erradicar a terra\Nimprópria para este céu,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.03,0:26:40.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and change everything\Nback to how it should be! -OG}{and return everything\Nback to how it should be! -T}e devolver tudo\Nà sua ordem natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.37,0:26:42.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That is my duty as God! -OG}Esse é...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.87,0:26:47.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse é meu dever como Deus!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.72,0:26:55.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I won't let you... -OG}Como se eu fosse deixar...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.72,0:27:00.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,fazer o que quer!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.27,0:27:10.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Adeus, homem de borracha!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.36,0:27:13.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Look on wistfully and\Nwait until the end arrives! -OG}{Look on with regret\Nand wait for the end to arrive! -T}{Look on wistfully as\Nyou wait for the end to arrive! -T}{Look on wistfully as you wait to die! -T+Rin}{Just sit tight and wait for\Nthe end to come! -T}Fique aí sentado e\Nespere o fim chegar!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.95,0:27:16.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.96,0:27:24.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.79,0:27:33.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ninguém... pode me parar agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.39,0:27:40.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Damn it! -OG}Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.43,0:27:44.81,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Listen! We will send you\Ninto the sky, without fail! -OG}Podem apostar, vocês estarão\Nvoando pelo céu amanhã!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.73,0:27:53.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.95,0:27:58.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I... -OG}{I will... -T}Eu vou...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.41,0:28:08.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{...will ring that bell! -OG}tocar aquele sino!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=11}===============================DIALOGUE============================
